            <div class="mdui-text-color-white-text mdui-color-theme mdui-typo-display-2 mdui-valign PostTitle" itemprop="name headline" itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting"><span class="mdui-center">唯识二十颂讲记</span></div>
